data.description: This sprawling rancher in the heart of Newport News has it all! Not only does it have an attached 2 car garage, it has an addition detached garage to provide ample space for projects or hobbies! New flooring in heated and cooled sunroom, making sure you can enjoy the feeling of the outdoors comfortable all year, and a fantastic space in rear of home for outdoor leisure. This wonderful home also features a den in addition to ample living area to have all the space your family needs. New appliances and new carpet make this the perfect space to call home!
